components.name: AppComponent
AutocompleteComponent
components.templateData:
<section class="autocomplete-container">
  <p-autoComplete [(ngModel)]="selectedValue" 
  [suggestions]="filteredValues" 
  [dropdown]="dropdown"
  [field]="filedName"
  [multiple]="multiple"
  [minLength]="minLength"
  [maxlength]="maxLength"
  (completeMethod)="filter($event)"
  ></p-autoComplete>
  <ng-template let-object pTemplate="item">
    {{ object.name }}
  </ng-template>
</section>

components.name: ButtonComponent
components.templateData:
<section class="button__container" [ngClass]="buttonId ? buttonId:''">
    <p-button 
    class="button__content"
    [ngClass]="{'transparent-button':transparentButton,
    'white-button': whiteButton}"
      [label]="label.toUpperCase()"
      [iconPos]="iconPos"
      [icon]="'pi ' + iconClassName"
      (click)="click()"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      >
    </p-button>
  </section>

components.name: CalendarComponent
components.templateData:
<section>
    <p-calendar
    [(ngModel)]="date"
    [showIcon]="showIcon"
    [showButtonBar]="showButtonBar"
    [readonlyInput]="readonlyInput"
    [showTime]="showTime"
    [showSeconds]="showSeconds"
    >Basic</p-calendar>
</section>

components.name: ChartBarsComponent
components.templateData:
<section class="chartBars-container">
    <p-chart type="bar" [data]="data" [options]="options"></p-chart>
</section>

components.name: CheckboxComponent
components.templateData:
<section class="checkbox--container">
    <p-checkbox 
    (onChange)="checkedTogglerEmiter()"
    [(ngModel)]="checked" 
    [binary]="true" 
    [disabled]="disabled"
    [label]="label">
    </p-checkbox>
</section>
